task.summary: Started fixing Xirgil, mostly by changing everything to lua abilities.

Started writing design documents for heroes, beginning with Flicker.
Also retuned Rapid Strike to have more consistent power gains on levelup.
Some rewording on Flicker's design doc.

Ability descriptions on Flicker's design doc are now consistent with in-game tooltips.
Improved wording on in-game tooltips.

My uncle gave me a bunch of hero concepts.
Also created blank hero documentation files for already-existing heroes.
